title: Short Ghost and Horror Collection 009
creator: Various
description: LibriVox recording of the Short Ghost and Horror Collection, volume 009. A collection of fifteen stories featuring ghoulies, ghosties, long-leggedy beasties and things that go bump in the night. Expect shivers up your spine, the stench of human flesh, and the occasional touch of wonder. For more free audio books or to become a volunteer reader, visit LibriVox.org. M4B format available
